headline: Halliburton awarded geothermal project by KS Orka Renewables
summary: Halliburton has received a multiyear contract from KS Orka Renewables Pte. Ltd to support geothermal well construction for the PT Sorik Marapi Geothermal Power and PT Sokoria Geothermal Indonesia projects in Indonesia.
